parameters:
Polka: "Huh, it's already 9 o'clock. Are you taking the day off from
school?"
Yui: "I overslept, I'm about to head to school now."
Yui: "Hmph! You bear some of the responsibility for this, Polka!"
Polka: "Don't we need to head to school soon?"

Polka: "If it's the Fols district, it's one station away from Daimon
Station, which is south of Daimon Shopping Street."
Polka: "I have a bad feeling about this. Be careful, Yui-chan."

Yui: (He said using telepathy drains his energy, maybe it's because of
what happened yesterday.)
Yui: (But... hehe, what a cute sleeping face.)

Yui: (When we first met, he was a bit of a brat, but somehow that's
turned into affection.)
Yui: (Has it already been half a year since I met Polka...)
Polka: "Hey, have you gained a little weight since I last saw you?"

Yui: "That's the first thing you say after such a long time!? Yes,
yes... I've gained weight!"
Yui: "I'm going to the gym, so let's drop that subject!"
Yui: "Does using telepathy really take up a lot of physical strength?"

Yui: "You've been sleeping longer than usual, you must be really
tired, right?"

Polka: "But I'm okay. Look, I'm fully recovered! I can even tell your
body shape clearly."
Yui: "I'm worried about you and you're making jokes..."
Yui: "I'm off to the gym now, so stay put in the basement, okay?"

\c[17]Let's head to Muscle Gym. (Muscle Gym is located in the Force
District.)\c[0]

Polka: "Thank you for worrying about me! Let's both do our best until
we annihilate Zaidar-G."

\c[17]Let's head to Muscle Gym. (Muscle Gym is located in the Forus
district.)\c[0]

Yui: "(He said using telepathy consumes his energy, so I should let
him be...)"
Polka is in a deep sleep and shows no signs of waking up.
Polka: "I'm so glad I was able to meet both Yui-chan and Ginga."
Polka: "I believe that the two of you can definitely defeat Darg-Noa."

Ginga: "Yui, what about the makeup exam? If you don't hurry, you'll
really be held back..."
There was nothing particularly new or interesting inside.

Polka: "Sorry, Yui-chan. I called you out even though we're in the
middle of class."
Yui: "Could it be that Zaidarugu's combatants have appeared?"

Polka: "This immense dark power... it's probably a high-ranking
officer or a monster from Zaidarugu."
Yui: "Polka, do you know the location?"

Polka: "I can't pinpoint the exact location, but I feel it coming from
the Fols district."

Yui: "The Fols district... That's right, the Yotsukoya Department
Store is also in the Fols district!"
Yui: "Sorry, Polka! I'm heading out now!"
Polka: "I have a bad feeling about this. Be careful, Yui-chan!"
Yui: "Pony Celes won't lose to anyone!"
There was nothing particularly new inside.
Yui: "That's right! I was saved by Polka..."
Yui: "What happened to Polka after that..."
